//-----------------------------
 Tutorial Case for mmcSprayFoam
//-----------------------------

Description
-----------
Piloted spray flames of Gounder and Masri(2010).


Reference
---------
A. R. Masri & J. D. Gounder (2010) Turbulent Spray Flames of Acetone and Ethanol Approaching Extinction, Combustion Science and Technology, 182:4-6, 702-715, DOI: 10.1080/00102200903467754

https://doi.org/10.1080/00102200903467754


MMC Publications on Spray
-------------------------
Nazmul Khan, Matthew J. Cleary, Oliver T. Stein, Andreas Kronenburg,
A two-phase MMC–LES model for turbulent spray flames,
Combustion and Flame,
Volume 193,
2018,
Pages 424-439,
ISSN 0010-2180,
https://doi.org/10.1016/j.combustflame.2018.03.023.
(http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0010218018301330)



